{"tid":146271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美食車拍烏蠅 官稱規則早定","createTime":"2017-03-07T03:00:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T12:04:52.000Z","uid":77196,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"76a415348bc8c93ad5352bb79a3a75ab174cdffd","tid":146271,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T03:00:21.000Z","msg":"有美食車經營者近日批評先導計劃，指顧客少，生意差。旅遊事務署昨日回應，若美食車如其中一些營運者所倡議，能隨意於街道售賣食物，除恐怕造成人流及車流阻礙外，更對現時已需要負擔相當租金及營運成本的食肆造成影響。而現有以抽籤方式決定輪流到8個指定地方營運的方式，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>營運者在投入服務前，已清楚這些規則</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n旅遊事務署建議營運者可按其策略推出切合不同場地顧客需要的其他菜式，計劃亦容許把顧客訂購的食物送往美食車以外目的地，即可以更改菜式和兼營送外賣。<br />\n<br />\nSource : HKEJ<br />\n<br />\n輸打贏要，執柒左去啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34e15263251c79b4329e5621b7a0cf23b155c56","tid":146271,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T03:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cda3d3640e1ff193c45267ffeb10aa9f5b8dd953","tid":146271,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T03:04:09.000Z","msg":"又要做又要人地俾你實賺到錢,明明做之前就講明固定地點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fedacb0693d8615265e4e72196ce905d9d2eb0b","tid":146271,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T03:05:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又要做又要人地俾你實賺到錢,明明做之前就講明固定地點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身諗住政府搞實無死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2557f550831bf80a26d99e1ad6a1cc4d16a51f68","tid":146271,"uid":18465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T03:05:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又要做又要人地俾你實賺到錢,明明做之前就講明固定地點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\